        <num>CC 815</num>
        <heading>815.  Partition by licitation</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 815.  Partition by licitation
When a thing is partitioned by licitation, a mortgage, lien, or privilege that burdens the share of a co-owner attaches to his share of the proceeds of the sale.</p>
        </content>
